OL,3,CAccidental Team GB Olympian pays
OL,4,Ctribute to late mum after two bronze
OL,5,Cwins
OL,7,FAs athlete Sam Reardon watched the
OL,8,Fopening ceremony from his sofa, little
OL,9,Fdid he realise just days later he
OL,10,Fwould not only be competing, but
OL,11,Fwinning medals, as ITV News' Antoine
OL,12,FAllen reports
OL,14,FTeam GB athlete Sam Reardon told ITV
OL,15,FNews "it meant the world" to win two
OL,16,Fbronze medals at the Paris Olympics -
OL,17,Fpaying tribute to his mum who died
OL,18,Fbefore seeing her son achieve their
OL,19,Fshared dream.
