OL,3,CAccidental Team GB Olympian pays
OL,4,Ctribute to late mum after two bronze
OL,5,Cwins
OL,7,FThe 20-year-old was not originally
OL,8,Fselected to be in Paris, but an injury
OL,9,Fto another member of Team GB meant he
OL,10,Fgot a last minute call to go to the
OL,11,FOlympics, with Reardon going on to win
OL,12,Ftwo bronze medals in the men's and
OL,13,Fmixed 400m relay.
OL,15,F"I was watching the opening ceremony
OL,16,Fin my room at home thinking ah damn, I
OL,17,Fwish I could have been there," he said.
