OL,7,F"(It went from) it's not happening but
OL,8,FI wish I could have been there, to
OL,9,Fbeing there and running - and coming
OL,10,Faway and winning two bronze medals,"
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,FHowever, Reardon's biggest fan was
OL,14,Fmissing from the crowd to celebrate
OL,15,Fhis special moment.
OL,17,FHis mum died from a brain tumour when
OL,18,Fhe was just 15 years old. She always
OL,19,Fhad unwavering belief her son would
OL,20,Fone day become an Olympian.
