OL,12,F"A hug from her would mean the world
OL,13,Fto me," he said.
OL,15,F"If I got to see her and I'd give her
OL,16,Fa hug and tell her how thankful I am
OL,17,Ffor everything, because I was quite
OL,18,Fyoung when she passed.
OL,20,F"I wasn't really coming to terms with
OL,21,Fit when I was 15 years old."
