OL,4,Ctribute to late mum after two bronze
OL,5,Cwins
OL,7,FEach time he stepped onto the podium,
OL,8,Fhe carried a picture of his mum in his
OL,9,Fpocket.
OL,11,F"She's here right on this podium with
OL,12,Fme," he continued.
OL,14,F"I felt that in myself, in my heart
OL,15,Falready, but to have that in physical
OL,16,Fform as well in way, it meant the
OL,17,Fworld.
OL,19,F"I know she would have loved to have
OL,20,Fbeen there and she would be screaming."
