OL,3,CAccidental Team GB Olympian pays
OL,4,Ctribute to late mum after two bronze
OL,5,Cwins
OL,7,FBy the time of the LA Olympics in
OL,8,F2028, Sam will be 24 years old and he
OL,9,Faims to fulfill one more promise to
OL,10,Fhis mum.
OL,12,F"She always said one day she wanted to
OL,13,Fsee me on top of the podium singing
OL,14,Fthe national anthem," Reardon said.
OL,16,F"She said she'd be balling her eyes
OL,17,Fout. So that's the ultimate aim, its
OL,18,Fto get on top of that and I think with
OL,19,Fthat sort of motivation I can
OL,20,Fdefinitely get there."
